<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Registratiefout</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Spartan:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Spartan', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #e4eef2;
      color: #002333;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }
    .container {
      background: #f8fbfc;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 35, 51, 0.1);
      border-radius: 12px;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e63946;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #002333;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .platform-url {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #007bff;
      word-wrap: break-word;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }
    .button-container {
      margin-top: 1.8rem;
    }
    .close-button {
      background-color: #002333;
      font-family: 'Spartan', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 48px 12px 48px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .close-button:hover {
      background-color: #00e075;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 224, 117, 0.2);
    }
    .copyright {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #778899cf;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 0px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="title">Er is een fout opgetreden</h1>
    <p class="message">Het lijkt erop dat de Eduface LTI Tool al is geregistreerd voor deze LMS-omgeving. Neem contact met ons op voor ondersteuning.</p>
    <p class="platform-url"><%= details.platformUrl %></p>
    <div class="button-container">
      <button class="close-button" onclick="window.close()">Sluit venster</button>
    </div>
    <p class="copyright">Â© 2024 Eduface B.V.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
